<hgroup><h1>DisC<sup>2</sup>o-HD: Distributed causal inference with covariates shift for analyzing real-world high-dimensional data</h1></hgroup><div class="cg p">
<a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Tong%20J"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id1"><span class="name western">Jiayi Tong</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id1">
<h3><span class="name western">Jiayi Tong</span></h3>
<div class="p">
<sup>1</sup>Department of Biostatistics, Epidemiology and Informatics, University of Pennsylvania, Philadelphia, PA 19104, USA</div>
<div class="p">Find articles by <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Tong%20J"[Author]' class="usa-link"><span class="name western">Jiayi Tong</span></a>
</div>
</div>
<sup>1,</sup><sup>*</sup>, <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Hu%20J"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id2"><span class="name western">Jie Hu</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id2">
<h3><span class="name western">Jie Hu</span></h3>
<div class="p">
<sup>2</sup>Department of Biostatistics, Epidemiology and Informatics, University of Pennsylvania, Philadelphia, PA 19104, USA</div>
<div class="p">Find articles by <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Hu%20J"[Author]' class="usa-link"><span class="name western">Jie Hu</span></a>
</div>
